variables.input:
fetch dt.entity.kubernetes_cluster
| sort lower(entity.name) asc
| fields entity.name
| LIMIT 25

fetch dt.entity.cloud_application_namespace
| filterOut matchesPhrase(entity.name, "openshift*")
| filterOut matchesPhrase(entity.name, "kube*")
| sort lower(entity.name) asc
| fields entity.name
| LIMIT 50

15.title: Running Pods
15.query:
timeseries max(dt.kubernetes.pods), alias: pods, by: {k8s.workload.name}, filter: k8s.cluster.name == $cluster AND k8s.namespace.name == $namespace AND pod_phase == "Running" AND pod_condition == "Ready"
| summarize pods = sum(arrayLast(pods))

16.title: Container CPU Usage
16.query:
timeseries avg(dt.containers.cpu.usage_percent), alias: cpu, by: {dt.entity.container_group_instance}
| lookup [fetch dt.entity.container_group_instance
  | fieldsAdd namespace = belongs_to[dt.entity.cloud_application_namespace]
  | lookup [fetch dt.entity.cloud_application_namespace
    | filter entity.name == $namespace
    | fieldsAdd cluster = clustered_by[dt.entity.kubernetes_cluster]
    | lookup [fetch dt.entity.kubernetes_cluster
      | filter entity.name == $cluster]
      ,sourceField: cluster, lookupField: id, prefix: "cluster."]
    , sourceField: namespace, lookupField: id, prefix: "namespace."
    | filter namespace.cluster == namespace.cluster.id
  | filter namespace == namespace.id],sourceField: dt.entity.container_group_instance, lookupField: id, prefix: "container."
| filterOut isNull(container.id)
| fields cpu, container.entity.name, alias: container, timeframe, interval

17.title: Container Mem Usage
17.query:
timeseries avg(dt.containers.memory.usage_percent), alias: mem, by: {dt.entity.container_group_instance}
| lookup [fetch dt.entity.container_group_instance
  | fieldsAdd namespace = belongs_to[dt.entity.cloud_application_namespace]
  | lookup [fetch dt.entity.cloud_application_namespace
    | filter entity.name == $namespace
    | fieldsAdd cluster = clustered_by[dt.entity.kubernetes_cluster]
    | lookup [fetch dt.entity.kubernetes_cluster
      | filter entity.name == $cluster]
      ,sourceField: cluster, lookupField: id, prefix: "cluster."]
    , sourceField: namespace, lookupField: id, prefix: "namespace."
    | filter namespace.cluster == namespace.cluster.id
  | filter namespace == namespace.id],sourceField: dt.entity.container_group_instance, lookupField: id, prefix: "container."
| filterOut isNull(container.id)
| fields mem, container.entity.name, alias: container, timeframe, interval

20.title: Desired Pods
20.query:
timeseries max(dt.kubernetes.workload.pods_desired), alias: pods, by: {k8s.workload.name}, filter: k8s.cluster.name == $cluster AND k8s.namespace.name == $namespace
| summarize pods = sum(arrayLast(pods))

21.title: Unhealthy Pods
21.query:
timeseries max(dt.kubernetes.pods), alias: pods, by: {k8s.workload.name}, filter: k8s.cluster.name == $cluster AND k8s.namespace.name == $namespace AND (pod_phase != "Running" OR pod_condition != "Ready")
| summarize pods = sum(arrayLast(pods))

22.title: Container Mem Limits
22.query:

| lookup [fetch dt.entity.container_group_instance
  | fieldsAdd namespace = belongs_to[dt.entity.cloud_application_namespace]
  | lookup [fetch dt.entity.cloud_application_namespace
    | filter entity.name == $namespace
    | fieldsAdd cluster = clustered_by[dt.entity.kubernetes_cluster]
    | lookup [fetch dt.entity.kubernetes_cluster
      | filter entity.name == $cluster]
      ,sourceField: cluster, lookupField: id, prefix: "cluster."]
    , sourceField: namespace, lookupField: id, prefix: "namespace."
    | filter namespace.cluster == namespace.cluster.id
  | filter namespace == namespace.id],sourceField: dt.entity.container_group_instance, lookupField: id, prefix: "container."
| filterOut isNull(container.id)
| fields mem, container.entity.name, alias: container, timeframe, interval

23.title: Workload CPU Requests
23.query: timeseries avg(dt.kubernetes.workload.requests_cpu), alias: cpu, by: {k8s.workload.name}, filter: k8s.cluster.name ==$cluster AND k8s.namespace.name == $namespace

24.title: Workload Mem Requests
24.query: timeseries avg(dt.kubernetes.workload.requests_memory), alias: mem, by: {k8s.workload.name}, filter: k8s.cluster.name ==$cluster AND k8s.namespace.name == $namespace

25.title: Container Restarts
25.query:
timeseries sum(dt.kubernetes.container.restarts), alias: restarts, by: {k8s.container.name, k8s.workload.name}, filter: k8s.cluster.name == $cluster AND k8s.namespace.name == $namespace
| fields restarts = arraySum(restarts), k8s.container.name, k8s.workload.name, timeframe, interval

26.title: Namespace CPU Quota - Requests
26.query:
fetch dt.entity.cloud_application_namespace
| filter entity.name == $namespace
| fieldsAdd cluster = clustered_by[dt.entity.kubernetes_cluster]
| lookup [fetch dt.entity.kubernetes_cluster | filter entity.name == $cluster 
  | fields id, entity.name], sourceField: cluster, lookupField: id, prefix: "cluster."
| lookup [timeseries max(dt.kubernetes.resourcequota.requests_cpu), alias: requests_cpu, by: {k8s.namespace.name}, filter: k8s.cluster.name == $cluster AND k8s.namespace.name == $namespace
  | fields last = arrayLast(requests_cpu), k8s.namespace.name], sourceField: entity.name, lookupField: k8s.namespace.name, prefix: "requests_cpu."
| fields requests_cpu.last

37.title: Recent Events (25)
37.query:
fetch logs
| filter event.type == "K8S" AND matchesValue(dt.kubernetes.cluster.name,$cluster) AND matchesValue(k8s.namespace.name,$namespace)
| fields timestamp, status, content, dt.kubernetes.event.involved_object.name, alias: object, dt.kubernetes.event.involved_object.kind, alias: object_kind, dt.event.group_label, alias: group_label
| sort timestamp desc
| LIMIT 25
